::Cygnar::
       He just stands there dumbfounded.  He mutters to himself in a voice no 
one can hear.  "When you et yourself killed to come crawling to me.  On the 
plus side at least I'll get command when he's dead."  He shrugs.  Either way 
he'd be happy.
